column5: There are lots of opportunities out there waiting for you. You don't have to blame yourself from everything you had done wrong because it might only ruin your life as a person. You see, a lot of people kind of feel on the same thing as you are. But I tell you, you don't have to kill yourself because I'm pretty sure someone will embrace your will.
